    'DK' => ['footer_note' => "<h3>Revolutionizing E-commerce in Denmark with Selldone Business OS</h3>\n\n<p>For the forward-thinking merchants of Denmark, the future of e-commerce is here. Selldone Business OS presents a seamless, no-plugin e-commerce platform tailored to the unique needs and ecosystem of Danish businesses. Whether you're selling products, services, subscriptions, or files, Selldone has got you covered.</p>\n\n<h3>Your E-commerce, Your Domain</h3>\n<p>With Selldone, Danish merchants can proudly claim their digital space. Every e-commerce site is hosted on your own domain, ensuring brand consistency and trustworthiness.</p>\n\n<h3>Effortless Setup for Danish Merchants</h3>\n<p>Forget the hassles of buying hosting or spending on plugins and templates. Selldone offers an easy setup process, allowing businesses in Denmark to focus on what they do best: selling.</p>\n\n<h3>Fully Compatible Tax Calculation</h3>\n<p>Understanding the intricacies of Denmark's tax system, Selldone comes equipped with tax calculation features tailored for the country, ensuring compliance without the complications.</p>\n\n<h3>For the Fast-Growing Brands of Denmark</h3>\n<p>Selldone isn't just for startups. It's designed for scalability, making it the perfect choice for rapidly expanding companies and iconic brands in Denmark.</p>\n\n<h3>Optimized for Sales and Conversion</h3>\n<p>Every feature in Selldone is crafted with one goal in mind: to boost your sales. From its intuitive design to its user-friendly interface, it's all about ensuring maximum conversion for Danish merchants.</p>\n\n<h3>Incentives Galore</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b>: Offer special prices to loyal customers.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b>: Entice new customers with limited-time deals.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b>: Maximize each transaction's value.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b>: Let your customers share the love.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing and Campaigns</h3>\n<p>Stay ahead of the competition with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. Reach out to your Danish audience effectively and efficiently, ensuring they always have a reason to come back.</p>\n\n<h3>Why Selldone Stands Out in Denmark</h3>\n\n<h3>Compared to WooCommerce</h3>\n<p>While WooCommerce requires hosting and often presents a less-than-ideal user experience, Selldone offers a streamlined, user-friendly platform. No more settling for subpar UI/UX.</p>\n\n<h3>Benefits Over Traditional E-commerce Platforms</h3>\n<p>Platforms like Shopify, Salesforce, and Magento often necessitate the installation of numerous plugins and templates. This not only complicates the user experience but also poses risks:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Sharing</b> with third parties can compromise your business's security.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> can disrupt your e-commerce operations.</li>\n    <li><b>Complexity</b> can deter potential customers and reduce sales.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>With Selldone, Danish merchants can enjoy a hassle-free, secure, and efficient e-commerce experience.</p>\n\n<h3>Embrace the Future of E-commerce in Denmark</h3>\n<p>It's time for Danish merchants to step into the future with Selldone Business OS. Experience the difference of a platform designed with your needs in mind.</p>\n"],
